{"tid":2166524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇下兩年前林鄭點講美國","createTime":"2020-08-20T13:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T13:12:09.000Z","uid":69231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"614b633e6fc757b0e485f4d38b90ea6ded7004f4","tid":2166524,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"2018.10.11<br />\n<br />\n她接著說：「今日美國政府往往做單邊主義，我們非常有意見，因為我們是最支持自由貿易其中一員，也是世貿成員之一。」<br />\n<br />\n因此，對有人提出不利香港的事，「我們會據理力爭」。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，貿易和投資是互惠的，香港並非從美國取得很多好處；香港是美國全球貿易順差最高的經濟體，現有130多家美國公司在港設立地區總部或辦事處等，這是港美的共同利益，需要雙方共同維護。（編輯：朱建陵）<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-10-11/151178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2018-10-11%2F151178&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5QsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=d152ce3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-10-11/151178</a><br />\n<br />\n而家睇返真係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2819f5175b9b40a6af511a5c256f89615333e2b","tid":2166524,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:09:21.000Z","msg":"而家你玩單機主義得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c517c224bd26a16c93ee0e3cb9d941990862f148","tid":2166524,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"臭雞又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}